title: Superfood
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In a city with limited pure veg food, this place offers some vegetarian dishes, and the owner-chef is committed to providing and adapting dishes to cater to vegetarians and vegans. Located a 10-minute drive (half hour walk up the hill) from the city centre, and has a terrace overlooking a quiet neighborhood street. Sometimes hosts live music.
